      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "昨日、書店で買った優おすすめの漫画はどうだった？\nん、瑠依？　なんだか眠そうだけど……",
      "startTime": 6.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "あ……お疲れ様です。実は昨日帰ってから\nつい……全巻、一気読みしてしまって……",
      "startTime": 14.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "一気読み！？　全部でニ十巻はあったのに？\nそんなに内容が良かったのか……？",
      "startTime": 21.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "はい。私、サキュバスってエッチで品がないものだと\n思ってましたけど……漫画を読んで印象が変わりました",
      "startTime": 28.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "まだ、ちゃんとは掴み切れていませんけど\nあの漫画に出てくるサキュバスは、一途で一生懸命で",
      "startTime": 35.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "今なら、私が演じるサキュバスのことも\n真っ直ぐに分かってあげられる気がするんです",
      "startTime": 43.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "その意気だ、瑠依ならきっと\n最高のサキュバスを演じられるはずだ",
      "startTime": 48.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "さ、最高のサキュバスってなんですか？　でもファンや\n{user}さんの期待に、応えてみせます",
      "startTime": 56.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "収録が始まるまでに、しっかり役を作り込んで\nものにしてみせますから！",
      "startTime": 63.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ゲームの収録三回目",
      "startTime": 66.0628799675,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1566.6692098000112,
          "startTime": 67.6295491773
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さんお疲れ様です\n様子を見に来てくれたんですね、ありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 71.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、もうそろそろ収録も佳境だろう？\n調子はどうだ？",
      "startTime": 78.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……最初に脚本をいただいた時は\n私、この役作りに凄く迷走していて……",
      "startTime": 84.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが、私にピッタリな役だと\n言った時も、何を言ってるんだろうって思いました",
      "startTime": 91.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……す、すまない\nあの時は、言葉が全然足りていなかったな……",
      "startTime": 96.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今なら、あの時の言葉の意味が分かります\nこのゲームのサキュバスは、私なんです",
      "startTime": 104.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "傲慢で、高潔で、プライドが高くて……\nでも努力をいとわないし、妥協もしない",
      "startTime": 111.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "目標に一直線で、譲れないもののためなら\nいくらでも粘って、頑張って……",
      "startTime": 118.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "彼女を知れば知るほど、自分に似てると思ったんです\nそうしたらいつの間にか、恥じらいはなくなってました",
      "startTime": 126.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "このサキュバスは、もう一人の私なんだって\n今はそう思っています",
      "startTime": 133.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "だから、私の精一杯のサキュバスを\nファンの人達に、全力で届けるつもりです",
      "startTime": 138.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "もう恥ずかしがっている瑠依はいないんだな\n今の瑠依は、自信があって、凄くカッコいいよ",
      "startTime": 145.4392655604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、ありがとうございます。そろそろ収録に\n戻りますね。ゲームの完成、楽しみにしていて下さい",
      "startTime": 152.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ゲームリリース記念イベント当日",
      "startTime": 158.2761570846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ。ゲームの中だけじゃなく、ステージでも\nサキュバスになるなんて……思いもしませんでした",
      "startTime": 165.166675822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "よく似合ってるよ、瑠依。それにその衣装のデザインも\nファンの人達の投票で決まったものだろう？",
      "startTime": 173.9333424886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "それはそうですけど、でも、この格好で人前に出るのは\n別問題です。さすがに少し……恥ずかしいです",
      "startTime": 181.2386383023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、ファンの人達が考えてくれたユニット名と\n衣装ですから……胸を張ってステージに立たないと",
      "startTime": 190.0000091553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-rui020.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、私、ゲームのようなカッコいいサキュバスに\n見えますか？　あ、でもあんまり見つめないで下さい！",
      "startTime": 198.4040479753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "み、見ていいのか悪いのか、どっちなんだ……？\nただ、そうだな。凄くカッコいいサキュバスに見えるよ",
      "startTime": 206.5666819255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
